About Manatee Springs RV Park
Welcome to Manatee Springs RV Park — a 55 & up, newly renovated retreat nestled in the heart of Chiefland, Florida. Tucked beneath the shade of towering live oaks and whispering pines, our park offers the charm of peaceful country living with all the comforts of home.
Our beautifully landscaped grounds feature 32 spacious RV sites, thoughtfully arranged to blend with the natural setting. Each site offers ample space — whether you’re pulling in with a cozy teardrop camper or a full-size Class A motorhome, you’ll have plenty of room to relax and unwind.
Our on-site managers help ensure the park stays clean, safe, and welcoming year-round. Every site includes full hookups with water, sewer, and electric. We offer flexible stay options including daily, short-term, and long-term monthly rates.
Click here to view our rates.
Come relax under the oaks and experience the tranquil lifestyle that makes Manatee Springs RV Park a hidden gem in Chiefland.
